headline: Texas Deep Freeze Shutters Some Energy-Consuming Industry Sites
summary: With almost 10% of US natural gas production estimated to be offline due to the cold, much of the disruption is focused on gas.  Goodyear Bayport on Saturday shut its chemical plant in Pasadena, Texas, in preparation for the deep freeze, the company said Sunday in a posting on the Community Awareness Emergency Response website.
